00:57:59,200 --> 00:58:01,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Hwan Ki.</font>

567
00:58:08,470 --> 00:58:15,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang kalian berdua bicarakan seserius itu?</font>

568
00:58:15,740 --> 00:58:17,220
