573
00:59:36,530 --> 00:59:39,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau ingin aku mati, 'kan?</font>

574
00:59:39,370 --> 00:59:41,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Eun Yi Soo.</font>

575
00:59:42,080 --> 00:59:48,190
